---

<BaseLayout
  title="Porta Potty Rental Cost Guide 2025 | Pricing & Rates"
  description="Complete guide to porta potty rental costs in 2025. Compare prices for standard units, luxury trailers, ADA accessible, and more. Get accurate pricing estimates."
>
  <!-- Hero Section - Dark with gradient -->
  <section class="relative py-16 md:py-20 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-primary-900 to-slate-900"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/herotile.jpeg')] opacity-10 bg-cover bg-center"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <Breadcrumb items={breadcrumbs} class="mb-6 text-slate-400" />

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 rounded-full px-4 py-2 mb-6">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-white/90">2025 Updated Pricing</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Porta Potty Rental
          <span class="block text-blue-400">Cost Guide</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10">
          Understand what you'll pay for portable restroom rentals. Most providers charge the same rate whether you rent for 1 day or 7 days.
        </p>

        <!-- Quick Stats -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 md:gap-12">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">$125-$195</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Standard Unit / Week</div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-px h-12 bg-white/20 hidden md:block"></div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">$175-$400</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Standard Unit / Month</div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-px h-12 bg-white/20 hidden md:block"></div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">$50-$150</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-400">Typical Delivery Fee</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing Cards Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">
          Rental Pricing by Type
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">
          Daily/Weekly rates are the same - whether 1 day or 7 days
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pricing Cards Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        {pricingData.map((item) => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow overflow-hidden">
            <div class={`p-6 ${
              item.color === 'orange' ? 'bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-orange-600' :
              item.color === 'purple' ? 'bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-purple-600' :
              item.color === 'blue' ? 'bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600' :
              item.color === 'yellow' ? 'bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-500 to-yellow-600' :
              item.color === 'green' ? 'bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600' :
              'bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600'
            } text-white`}>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                <span class="text-3xl">{item.icon}</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-medium bg-white/20 px-2 py-1 rounded-full">{item.useCase}</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">{item.type}</h3>
              <p class="text-sm opacity-90 mt-1">{item.description}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
                <div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide">Daily/Weekly</div>
                  <div class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">{item.dailyWeekly}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-right">
                  <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide">Monthly</div>
                  <div class="text-xl font-bold text-green-600">{item.monthly}</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-xs text-gray-400 text-center border-t border-gray-100 pt-3">
                Same price for 1-7 days
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- Info Box -->
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-blue-600 font-semibold mb-2">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          How Pricing Works
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Most porta potty providers charge the same rate whether you need the unit for 1 day or 7 days. This "daily/weekly" rate is the industry standard. Monthly rates kick in for rentals longer than a week.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Factors Affecting Price - Dark Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-slate-900">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
          What Affects Your Price
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg">
          Understand the factors that influence rental costs
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {factors.map((factor) => (
          <div class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-700/50 hover:border-slate-600 transition-colors">
            <div class={`w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 ${
              factor.color === 'blue' ? 'bg-blue-500/20' :
              factor.color === 'purple' ? 'bg-purple-500/20' :
              factor.color === 'orange' ? 'bg-orange-500/20' :
              factor.color === 'yellow' ? 'bg-yellow-500/20' :
              factor.color === 'green' ? 'bg-green-500/20' :
              'bg-red-500/20'
            }`}>
              <svg class={`w-6 h-6 ${
                factor.color === 'blue' ? 'text-blue-400' :
                factor.color === 'purple' ? 'text-purple-400' :
                factor.color === 'orange' ? 'text-orange-400' :
                factor.color === 'yellow' ? 'text-yellow-400' :
                factor.color === 'green' ? 'text-green-400' :
                'text-red-400'
              }`} fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d={factor.icon} />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">{factor.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">{factor.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's Included Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">
          What's Typically Included
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">
          Know what to expect with your rental
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Included -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-lg p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Usually Included</h3>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {['Weekly cleaning and servicing', 'Waste pump-out and disposal', 'Toilet paper restocking', 'Hand sanitizer refills', 'Deodorizer treatment', 'Basic delivery and pickup'].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600">{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Extra Cost -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-lg p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Often Extra Cost</h3>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {['Rush delivery (same-day/next-day)', 'Long-distance delivery fees', 'Extra servicing (2-3x per week)', 'Holiday or weekend delivery', 'Damage/cleaning fees', 'Stairs or difficult placement'].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-600">{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tips Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-slate-900">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-3">
          Tips for Getting the Best Price
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg">
          Smart strategies to save money on your rental
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-700/50 flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-primary-400 font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Book Early</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Reserve 2-3 weeks ahead, especially for peak season. Last-minute bookings cost more.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-700/50 flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-primary-400 font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Get Multiple Quotes</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Prices vary significantly between providers. Compare at least 3 quotes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-700/50 flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-primary-400 font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Choose Monthly Rates</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">For rentals over 2 weeks, monthly rates offer significant savings vs. weekly rates.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-700/50 flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-500/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-primary-400 font-bold">4</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Ask About Bundles</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Renting multiple units or adding hand wash stations? Ask for package discounts.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-blue-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Ready to Get an Exact Quote?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Use our calculator to estimate your needs, then find providers in your area for accurate quotes.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/calculator" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-primary-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-primary-600/25">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 14h.01M12 14h.01M15 11h.01M12 11h.01M9 11h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
          Use Calculator
        </a>
        <a href="/states" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border-2 border-gray-300 text-gray-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
          Find Providers
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SEO Content -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Understanding Porta Potty Rental Costs</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Portable toilet rental prices depend on many factors, but understanding the basics will help you budget
        accurately for your event or job site. Most providers charge the same rate for daily and weekly rentals
        (1-7 days), with monthly rates offering better value for longer-term needs.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 mt-8">Standard vs. Luxury Units</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Standard porta potties are the most affordable option, typically running $125-$195 for daily/weekly rental or $175-$400 per month.
        These include basic amenities like toilet paper and hand sanitizer. Luxury restroom trailers with
        climate control, flushing toilets, and running water cost significantly more ($1,200-$2,000 per week)
        but provide a much better guest experience for weddings and upscale events.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 mt-8">Hidden Costs to Watch For</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Always ask about delivery fees, pickup fees, and servicing frequency. Some providers include delivery
        within a certain radius, while others charge $50-$150 or more. Rush deliveries (same-day or next-day)
        typically cost extra. For multi-day events, confirm whether daily servicing is included or extra.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 mt-8">OSHA Requirements for Construction Sites</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        Construction sites must comply with OSHA regulations for portable toilets. The number required depends
        on the number of workers: 1 toilet for up to 20 workers, 2 for 20-35 workers, and so on. Failing to
        provide adequate facilities can result in fines.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
